'''阿馬多·卡里略·富恩特斯'''（Amado Carrillo Fuentes，{{bd|1956年|12月17日|1997年|7月7日}})是一个[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]毒枭，他在暗杀了他的老板{{link-en|拉斐尔·阿吉拉尔·瓜哈尔多|Rafael Aguilar Guajardo}}之后<ref name="frontera">{{Cite news|author=Getty, Mark|title=Mexico's Forgotten Disappeared: The Victims of the Border Narco Bloodbath|date=February 2004|url=http://www.nmsu.edu/~frontera/jan-feb04/feat1.html|work=Frontera NorteSur|accessdate=2010-09-25|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20121214195521/http://www.nmsu.edu/~frontera/jan-feb04/feat1.html|archivedate=2012-12-14}}</ref><ref name="Gonzalez">{{Cite news|author=González, Héctor A.|title=Los prófugos del salinato|date=February 21, 2007|url=http://www.red-ami.com/cgi-bin/ed_seccion.cgi?dt=21/02/2007&ref=20070221/090/20070220-132332.txt|work=El Diario|accessdate=2010-09-25|language=es|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120313032234/http://www.red-ami.com/cgi-bin/ed_seccion.cgi?dt=21%2F02%2F2007&ref=20070221%2F090%2F20070220-132332.txt|archivedate=March 13, 2012}}</ref>，夺取了{{link-en|华雷斯卡特尔|Juárez Cartel}}的控制权。阿馬多·卡里略·富恩特斯被称为El Señor de Los Cielos（天空之主），因为他用大型[[喷气式飞机|喷气式飞机]]运送毒品。為了資助飛機運輸隊，他还通过[[哥伦比亚|哥伦比亚]][[洗钱|洗钱]]。墨西哥和美国当局開始對其展開追踪。1997年7月，他在接受了[[整形外科|整形外科]]手術后，於墨西哥一家医院去世<ref>{{Cite news|title=DEA Map of Juarez Cartel operations|date=February 1997|url=https://www.pbs.org/wgbh/pages/frontline/shows/mexico/family/juarezcartel.html|work={{link-en|Frontline (U.S. TV series)}}|publisher=PBS|accessdate=2012-02-23|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126055716/https://www.pbs.org/wgbh/pages/frontline/shows/mexico/family/juarezcartel.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|author=Dillon, Sam|title=Drug Barons and Plastic Surgeons: Who's Dead, Who's Hiding?|date=November 7, 1997|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1997/11/07/world/drug-barons-and-plastic-surgeons-who-s-dead-who-s-hiding.html?ref=amajdocarrillofuentes|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2012-02-23|archive-date=2020-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200315190718/https:/